## 6. Planning View (Main Canvas)

### 6.1 Semantic Zoom Levels

The canvas morphs based on zoom level - "Google Earth for time."

| Level | Zoom | Time Scale | Visualization | Purpose |
|-------|------|-----------|---------------|---------|
| **MACRO** | < 0.5x | 10-12 years | Heatmap cells | Strategic planning |
| **MESO** | 0.5x - 2.0x | 1-3 years | Task blocks | Tactical planning |
| **MICRO** | > 2.0x | 1-8 weeks | Detailed cards | Operational planning |

